title: The Veils b-sides & rarities compiled
description:
The Veils. b-sides, rarities, etc. 

25 tracks culled from:

Lavinia CD single
The Tide That Left & Never Came Back CD single
The Wild Son CD single
More Heat Than Light CD single
Guiding Light CD single
Troubles Of The Brain EP

+ live session tracks "Turn Me On" (Nina Simone cover), "State Trooper" (Springsteen), "You Belong To Me" (Bob Dylan), and "Clap Hands" (Tom Waits). A couple demos thrown in for good measure, including rarities "H.O.L.L.A.N.D." and "In Dreams", etc.
